### 代码

```java
class Solution {
    public int arraySign(int[] nums) {
        //int product=0;
        int count=0;
        for(int i=0;i<nums.length;i++){
            if(nums[i]==0){
                return 0;

            }else if(nums[i]<0){
                count++;
            }
        }
        if(count%2==0){
            return 1;
        }else {
            return -1;
        }
    }
}



